title: Seattle City Council 2/10/20
description: Agenda: Public Comment; Payment of Bills; CB 119726: relating to termination of residential rental tenancies, prohibiting evictions in winter months; Res 31930: regarding Seattle Police Officer's Guild (SPOG) 2021 contract renewal; Appointments to Levy to Move Seattle Oversight Committee, Seattle City Employees' Retirement System Board, Labor Standards Advisory Commission.
